ingredientsDesc:
ARCHITECT Anti-CCP Reagent kit (100/500 Tests)
Microparticles 1 Bottle (6.5 mL/26.5 mL) CCP coated microparticles in phosphate buffer with surfactant and protein stabilizer.

Conjugate 1 Bottle (5.8 mL/25.8 mL) Mouse anti-human IgG:acridinium-labeled conjugate in MES buffer with surfactant and protein stabilizer.
Sample Diluent 1 Bottle (9.8 mL/50.0 mL) Phosphate buffer with surfactant and protein stabilizer.
ARCHITECT Anti-CCP Calibrators
6 Bottles (4.3 mL each) of ARCHITECT Anti-CCP Calibrators. The calibrators yield the following concentrations:
 Bottle	Anti-CCP Concentration (U/mL)	 Bottle	Anti-CCP Concentration (U/mL)
CAL A	0.0	CAL D	50.0
CAL B	5.0	CAL E	100.0
CAL C	25.0	CAL F	200.0

ARCHITECT Anti-CCP Controls
2 Bottles (7.0 mL each) of ARCHITECT Anti-CCP Controls. The controls yield the following homocysteine concentrations (U/mL):
Bottle	Anti-CCP Concentration (U/mL)	Range (U/mL)
CONTROL+	24.0	13.2 – 34.8
CONTROL -	0.1	≦1.6
